2hr actual vs 5hr planned)", "cumulative_efficiency_days_1-5": "250% average (10hr vs 25hr planned)", "recent_decisions": ["#142 Zen MCP boundary enforcement", "#141 ConPort progressive truncation", "#140 Desktop-Commander validated safe", "#139 Serena-v2 2-layer defense", "#138 System-wide audit"], "progress_tasks": ["#147 Restart Claude Code", "#148 Test in production", "#149 Monitor edge cases", "#150 Create shared utility", "#151 Add monitoring", "#152 Document best practices"], "completion_status": "100% of identified vulnerabilities resolved", "critical_fixes": {"fix_1": "Workspace detection - changed Path.cwd() to git root detection (workspace_utils.py)", "fix_2": "MCP server env vars - pass instance_env to subprocess (cli.py)", "fix_3": "Worktree isolation - use actual_workspace instead of main repo (instance_manager.py)", "fix_4": "Dynamic ports - enable multi-instance with ${CONPORT_PORT:-3004} pattern (docker-compose.yml)"}, "files_changed": ["src/dopemux/workspace_utils.py (NEW - 174 lines)", "src/dopemux/cli.py (5 changes)", "src/dopemux/instance_manager.py (workspace ID fix)", "docker/mcp-servers/docker-compose.yml (ConPort + Serena dynamic ports)", "WORKSPACE_MULTI_INSTANCE_FIX.md (NEW - documentation)"], "impact": "CRITICAL - Restored ADHD context preservation (was completely broken)", "backward_compatible": true, "testing_required": ["Single instance from subdirectory", "Multi-instance with worktrees", "Workspace isolation verification", "Port conflict resolution"], "ready_for_testing": true, "git_commit": "04a9b708", "git_message": "fix: Critical workspace detection and multi-instance isolation bugs", "files_committed": 16, "lines_committed": "+4712 -185", "commit_timestamp": "2025-10-19T18:32:59Z", "ready_for_push": true, "last_commit_message": "feat: Phase 2 Complete - Worktree Auto-Configuration (Zero Manual Steps)", "pushed_to_origin": true, "all_vulnerabilities_resolved": true, "commits_ahead_of_origin": 0, "days_completed": "1-10", "days_rema